EU’s Rehn Says Financial Crisis ‘Has Come to a New Phase’

-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 
2011-09-22T13:36:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/eu-s-rehn-says-financial-crisis-has-come-to-a-new-phase-.html
The European Union’s debt crisis is
in a “new phase,” EU Economic and Monetary Affairs
Commissioner  Olli Rehn  said.  “The financial and economic crisis which started three
years ago with the Lehman collapse has come to a new phase,”
Rehn said in the text of a speech today in  Washington .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
